{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras/About.png?t=1733785939\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A short, creepy, immersive and primordial experience</strong> that will bring you underground, in a completely unknown place, full of <strong>puzzles</strong> to solve, hunted by a ruthless being.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll find a\u00a0lot of <strong>metaphoric elements</strong>, meaningful details and different, philosophical and psichological <strong>interpretations</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixeled</strong> assets and minimal graphics were used here, precise and curated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story is simple, filled with references from <strong>movies</strong> (Pulp Fiction, Angel Heart, more), <strong>music</strong> (Dream Theater, Ne Obliviscaris, more) and <strong>oriental cultures</strong>.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is based on original, interesting, complex\u00a0<strong>puzzles</strong>, if you can't solve them, there's a walkthrough online I recorded for you, so that you can go on without getting bored!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>I worked hard and really put my soul in this, so...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/extras/Enjoy.png?t=1733785939\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733785939","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333110/page.bg.jpg?t=1733785939","capsul